Package ch.ethz.inf.vs.persistingservice.database.documents

Class Summary
Avg Avg is a couchdb document template to retrieve documents from the database containing the avg.
DateAvg DateAvg is a couchdb document template to retrieve documents from the database containing the avg, whenever a data was specified for data retrieval.
DateMax DateMax is a couchdb document template to retrieve documents from the database containing the max, whenever a data was specified for data retrieval.
DateMin DateMin is a couchdb document template to retrieve documents from the database containing the min, whenever a data was specified for data retrieval.
DateSum DateSum is a couchdb document template to retrieve documents from the database containing the sum, whenever a data was specified for data retrieval.
Default Default is a couchdb document template to retrieve documents from the database with all their information.
DefaultStorage<T extends Comparable> DefaultStorage is a document template, which is used to (only) store new documents in the database.
Max Max is a couchdb document template to retrieve documents from the database containing the max.
Min Min is a couchdb document template to retrieve documents from the database containing the min.
Sum Sum is a couchdb document template to retrieve documents from the database containing the sum.
